name: The Collins Cocktail Cabinet
description: A superlative cocktail cabinet, the Collins has a striking onyx back bar, glass storage shelves, a black marble preparation counter and an elegant exterior of black and pearl sycamores, with brushed brass detailing. The front cabinet doors glide open, revealing a striking back bar, glass display shelves and a granite top. The lower cabinets are lined in luxurious flock and incorporate sleek brushed brass handles.
